title: The Bleeders DIEgest Vault: The Feed (Guest Starring Spencer Charnas)

description:
All this month we invite you into the Bleeders DIEgest vault, a curated collection of some of our favorite stories. The host of a horror-themed podcast gets more than he bargained for with his latest guest. Guest-starring Spencer Charnas.
